                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Baltimore</placeName>\n                <date>April 63d/68</date>\n            </p>\n            <p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee>,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">My dear Sir,</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Faithful to my,<lb/> promise, I solicited subscriptions<lb/> to your\n                publications, but have<lb/> only succeeded in procuring a<lb/> single name. There\n                appears<lb/> (as you so clearly explained to<lb/> me, a want of manifest\n                inte<lb/>rest in Jewish publications, and<lb/> still less appreciation of\n                Jewish<lb/> authors. When oh when will<lb/> you receive the reward which your<lb/>\n                labours so e<add>?</add> entitle<lb/> you to receive. I fear not until<lb/> a new\n                spirit is infused in the<lb/> heart of <placeName>Israel</placeName>.</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3dr2pr7k/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
